\q1
\v 5  \add Then\add* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* idol \add stands there\add* \w like|strong="H3808"\w* [SIM] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w scarecrow|strong="H8560"\w* \w in|strong="H1696"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* field \w of|strong="H3372"\w* cucumbers/melons!  
