\b  
\p
\v 11  \add You Israeli people\add*, tell \w this|strong="H1836"\w* \w to|strong="H4481"\w* \w those|strong="H1768"\w* people: “\w Those|strong="H1768"\w* idols \w did|strong="H5648"\w* \w not|strong="H3809"\w* \w make|strong="H3809"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* \w sky|strong="H8065"\w* \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* earth, \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w they|strong="H1768"\w* \w will|strong="H1768"\w* disappear \w from|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* earth.”   
