\p
\v 12  \add So I told that message to the people\add*, \w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* replied, “\w It|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3820"\w* useless \add for you to tell us that\add*. \w We|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3820"\w* \add continue to\add* \w be|strong="H3820"\w* stubborn \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w behave|strong="H6213"\w* \w as|strong="H6213"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* want \w to|strong="H3212"\w*.”   
\p
