\s1 Jeremiah complained to Yahweh again  
\p
\v 7  \add One day I said this to Yahweh\add*:  
\q1 “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \add when you chose me to be a prophet,\add*\w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w deceived|strong="H6601"\w* \w me|strong="H2388"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w allowed|strong="H3201"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w deceive|strong="H6601"\w* \w me|strong="H2388"\w*.  
