\c 32  
\s1 Jeremiah bought some land  
\p
\v 1 \w After|strong="H1961"\w* \w Zedekiah|strong="H6667"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w been|strong="H1961"\w* ruling \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w for|strong="H3068"\w* almost ten \w years|strong="H8141"\w*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w* another \w message|strong="H1697"\w*, \w during|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w time|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5019"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w been|strong="H1961"\w* ruling \add Babylonia\add* \w for|strong="H3068"\w* almost 18 \w years|strong="H8141"\w*.  
