\v 5  \add At that time\add*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w army|strong="H2428"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \add Hophra\add*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w King|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w*, \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \add to the southern border of Judah\add*. \w When|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w army|strong="H2428"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Babylonia|strong="H3778"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H8085"\w*, \w they|strong="H5921"\w* stopped surrounding \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w and|strong="H3389"\w* \w left|strong="H3318"\w* \w there|strong="H5927"\w* \add to fight against the army from Egypt\add*.   
