\s1 Jeremiah was put into a prison  
\p
\v 11 \w When|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w army|strong="H2428"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w Babylonia|strong="H3778"\w* \w left|strong="H1961"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w army|strong="H2428"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* Egypt \w was|strong="H1961"\w* approaching,  
