\v 12-13 Nebuchadnezzar’s \add soldiers\add* will burn down the temples of the gods of Egypt. \add But before they burn the temples\add*, they will take away their idols \add as souvenirs\add*. His \add troops\add* will clean Egypt like \w a|strong="H3068"\w* shepherd cleans lice from his cloak. They will tear down the sacred pillars that are in the temple of their sun god. And then Nebuchadnezzar’s \add troops\add* will leave there, without having been harmed.” ’ ”   
\c 44  
\s1 Jeremiah predicted disaster would come because of their idolatry  
\p
\v 1  \add This is\add* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w message|strong="H1697"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w* \w concerning|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Jews|strong="H3064"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* \w living|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \add northern\add* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w*—\w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w Migdol|strong="H4024"\w*, Tahpenes, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w Memphis|strong="H5297"\w* \add cities\add*, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Pathros|strong="H6624"\w* \add region in southern Egypt\add*:  
\v 2 “\w This|strong="H2088"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w what|strong="H2088"\w* \add I\add*, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Commander \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w armies|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* angels, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* whom \add you\add* Israelis \add say you belong to\add*, \w say|strong="H3478"\w*: ‘\w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w disaster|strong="H7451"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w I|strong="H2005"\w* caused \add the people in\add* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w other|strong="H2088"\w* \w towns|strong="H5892"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w experience|strong="H7200"\w*. \w Those|strong="H3605"\w* \w towns|strong="H5892"\w* \w are|strong="H3117"\w* \w now|strong="H3117"\w* \w ruined|strong="H2723"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* deserted.  
\v 3  \add That happened\add* \w because|strong="H6440"\w* \w I|strong="H3045"\w* \w was|strong="H7451"\w* extremely \w angry|strong="H3707"\w* \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w them|strong="H1992"\w* \w on|strong="H6213"\w* \w account|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w their|strong="H6440"\w* being \w very|strong="H6213"\w* \w wicked|strong="H7451"\w*. \w They|strong="H1992"\w* \w burned|strong="H6999"\w* \w incense|strong="H6999"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* other gods \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w worshiped|strong="H5647"\w* \w them|strong="H1992"\w*. \w They|strong="H1992"\w* \w were|strong="H1992"\w* gods \w that|strong="H3045"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \add previously\add* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w about|strong="H6213"\w*, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w your|strong="H6440"\w* ancestors \w also|strong="H6213"\w* \add did not know about them\add*.  
\v 4 Many times \w I|strong="H1697"\w* \w sent|strong="H7971"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* \w prophets|strong="H5030"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w served|strong="H6213"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w*, \w to|strong="H7971"\w* \w say|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H7971"\w* \w them|strong="H7971"\w*, “\w Do|strong="H6213"\w* \w not|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w abominable|strong="H8441"\w* \w things|strong="H1697"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w I|strong="H1697"\w* \w hate|strong="H8130"\w*!”  
\v 5 \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w my|strong="H8085"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w would|strong="H7451"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w pay|strong="H5186"\w* \w any|strong="H3808"\w* \w attention|strong="H8085"\w* [DOU] \add to what I said to them\add*. \w They|strong="H3808"\w* \w would|strong="H7451"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w turn|strong="H7725"\w* \w away|strong="H7725"\w* \w from|strong="H7725"\w* \w their|strong="H8085"\w* \w wicked|strong="H7451"\w* behavior, \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w stop|strong="H3808"\w* \w burning|strong="H6999"\w* \w incense|strong="H6999"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \add worship/honor\add* \w other|strong="H1115"\w* gods.  
