\v 7 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \add I\add*, \w the|strong="H3541"\w* Commander \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3541"\w* \w armies|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* angels, \w the|strong="H3541"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* whom \add you\add* Israelis \add say you belong to\add*, ask \w you|strong="H6213"\w*: ‘\w Why|strong="H4100"\w* \w are|strong="H3478"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w causing|strong="H6213"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H5315"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* experience \w these|strong="H6213"\w* \w disasters|strong="H7451"\w*? \add Do you not realize that because of what you are doing\add*, \w soon|strong="H6258"\w* \w there|strong="H6258"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* \w no|strong="H6213"\w* \w more|strong="H1419"\w* \w men|strong="H1419"\w* \w or|strong="H1419"\w* \w women|strong="H7451"\w* \w or|strong="H1419"\w* \w children|strong="H5768"\w* \w or|strong="H1419"\w* \w infants|strong="H5768"\w* \w left|strong="H3498"\w* \w among|strong="H8432"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \add who have come here to Egypt\add* \w from|strong="H3772"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w*?  
